{"tid":956423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼海嘯增至429死　恐爆人道危機","createTime":"2018-12-26T08:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T13:35:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"24b5092998494f54f553fbbafe8df8731e083c50","tid":956423,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181226/20577184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F20577184&d=MVClInYvP9WegFKTBMkVBKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7f3badcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F20577184&h=07620802\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181226/20577184</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月26日 <br />\n<br />\n印尼海嘯增至429死　恐爆人道危機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181226/large/26wx5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181226%2Flarge%2F26wx5p.jpg&h=17fc3f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n災民抱着孩子看村子海嘯後滿目瘡痍情況。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n印尼海嘯死亡人數昨增至429人，近1,500人受傷，154人失蹤。救援人員正以徒手或挖掘機，從瓦礫堆中搜索被困者，當局亦派出無人機和搜索犬，但相信被困者生還機會渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潮漲當海嘯　村民慌忙逃上山<br />\n<br />\n有救援組織警告，清潔食水、藥物和糧食短缺，數千災民擠滿避難中心，恐爆發公共衞生危機。專家警告或將有更致命的海嘯來臨。逾5,000名災民不敢回家。有災民躲到高地避難，使救援難以送達。<br />\n<br />\n事發時正在海邊表演的流行樂隊Seventeen，前日為喪生的成員舉行喪禮，唯一倖存的主音法亞夏（Riefian Fajasyah），昨日為妻子薩哈拉（Dylan Sahara）落葬。<br />\n<br />\n專家指事故由離岸50公里的「喀拉喀托之子」火山爆發間接引起，使巽他海峽沿岸地區受海嘯沖擊，爪哇島與蘇門答臘之間的五村受襲，西岸萬丹省板底蘭成重災區。令次海嘯令沿岸居民成驚弓之鳥，楠榜省一條村的村民昨天誤以為潮漲是海嘯再來，數百人慌忙逃上山。<br />\n<br />\n德新社/法新社/路透社/美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n奇雲史帕西正式被控非禮少男<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n埃特納火山爆發　意機場交通受阻"},{"pid":"2f9d7d1de9424cf7c63cd19293560b0ffd2410ec","tid":956423,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7278867fc4850a04c70a3d4922af485ee4386ed9","tid":956423,"uid":2054,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"排華果時無人道危機？<br />\n政府咪撚捐錢呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"32b0770e6c27e782bb384ace8b4c47ee1b6d4eab","tid":956423,"uid":69886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"抵撚死垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6cb59374048097da33835e2330048fc37e74f3","tid":956423,"uid":25858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32b0770e6c27e782bb384ace8b4c47ee1b6d4eab","tid":956423,"uid":69886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"抵撚死垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a858caad096d6fb477bd9fcb27235592f37238","tid":956423,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c4c3452a01317e4d41dda13e81d7daacef3cef","tid":956423,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"陰公垃圾國家無人理"},{"pid":"c81fb4c206e02ceb75a802a65d4da3459b210ffd","tid":956423,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"其實東南亞仲係好落後"},{"pid":"eea6f2b42857ab0c06744f8937626f958f9fa5f2","tid":956423,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas again to Indonesia <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" clas